---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Work with me · Gerard Agba" description="I install n8n finance automation as a per-client white-label service for accounting firms serving CPG/DTC brands. Fixed-scope, 2 weeks.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-16">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-4">Work with me</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight">
      Per-client installs for accounting firms &mdash; or in-house finance at a DTC brand.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mt-6">
      You bring the client (or the brand). I build, deploy, and document the workflow on real data.
      Your bookkeepers stay in the relationship. No client poaching in writing.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Single Client Install &mdash; $4,500</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">
          One workflow installed on one of your clients' real data. Fixed scope, 2 weeks.
          Your firm stays the client's primary relationship. Pays back in 2&ndash;3 months of saved bookkeeping hours.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Firm Partnership &mdash; custom</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">
          White-label install service for your firm. I become your back-end automation specialist.
          You bill clients full price; I take a per-engagement fee. Multi-client volume pricing.
          Best for firms with 5+ CPG/DTC clients on a similar stack.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Custom Build &mdash; from $15,000</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">
          Bespoke workflow for a specific client problem outside the public template library.
          Includes specification, sample-data design, Python validation, n8n build, and a 1-page
          ownership-transfer doc for your team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <a
        href="https://calendly.com/agbagerard/n8n-reconciliation-sprint-discovery"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[color:var(--color-accent)] text-black font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition"
      >
        Book a discovery call →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
